CULTURA’18, Cultural and Technical Fest
 CMR institute of technology, Bangalore, Karnataka,
3rd – 4th April 2018

Fest Name: CULTURA’18

Fest Type: Cultural and technical
Organised By: CMR Institute of technology
Fest Date: 3rd and 4th April, 2018
Fest Details: Cultura’18 is an annual fest organised by CMR institute of technology. The fest witnesses participation from students across Bangalore. The fests has been star studded as previous years, Lagori, sunburn(lost stories), Dj Aerreo, The Raghu Dixit Project have performed. The technical events also receive incredible response.
